{"tid":1048456,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【由反叛變孝順】唔識劏劈落手指 開facebook吸客 童顏90後街市劏魚：最開心可以陪父母","createTime":"2019-03-05T15:58:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-06T00:10:58.000Z","uid":135867,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9795b35a459e35dffae09c8238bf87e77724d546","tid":1048456,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T15:58:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/MVskIlV4QRU\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FMVskIlV4QRU&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXh21egSez4RG9A7txFtatZY%3D&h=7d9af5c7\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/MVskIlV4QRU</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/vdo/20190226/720pix/1551178559_0c5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2Fvdo%2F20190226%2F720pix%2F1551178559_0c5d.jpg&h=1c821fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n「阿姐，要啲乜？」「總共$62，計你平啲，$60啦。」馬鞍山一個街市傳來年輕的叫賣聲。她是華記海鮮的太子女華女（Freda Lai）。「我小學的時候，爸媽就開始經營魚檔。」從沒有想過長大後，有一天會去店鋪幫忙。她本身有份穩定的職業，在婚紗店做婚禮顧問。「前年開始，爸媽身體陸續有許多毛病。」<br />\n<br />\n兩老手痛腳痛，有時痛得連手也舉不動。「還有，看見他們回家後累極而睡的樣子，真的很心痛。那時候就萌生一個念頭，不如我去幫輕他們。」這提議令父母都出乎意料，但也不反對。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華女肯學肯做，最成功的，要算在facebook開設專頁，讓人網上柯打之餘，亦可訂海鮮拼盤。只要說出價錢、人數，她就會搜羅時令海鮮，兼且做好前期的清潔工夫再入箱。客人買回家，即可打邊爐或燒烤，很方便。<br />\n<br />\n我以前有過很壞的時期，讀到中三左右，就停了學兩年。」那兩年她甚少回家，「現在回想，亦沒有解釋，可能要經歷過，才會長大。」<br />\n<br />\n「總之現在想多些時間陪伴他們，幫他們做事，那就很開心了。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n90後棄升學走進街市當「賣魚妹」　不介意魚腥味：只想幫輕父母【有片】<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2200000/2204610/fish_thumb_20181109_ch_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2200000%2F2204610%2Ffish_thumb_20181109_ch_600.jpg&h=9355bee2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/_taHwA-J3Tc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F_taHwA-J3Tc&d=tUmqA7E7lgkQFc9zeVIKXh21egSez4RG9A7txFtatZY%3D&h=559c7e2c\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/_taHwA-J3Tc</a><br />\n<br />\n喧鬧的叫賣聲、滿地的積水、難聞的魚腥味，許多年輕人對傳統街市都避之則吉，出生在90後、現年21歲的少女Apple去年考完DSE後卻選擇走入街市，在充滿魚腥味的攤檔上做個「賣魚妹」。Apple稱，魚檔是父母的心血，自己作為家中長女有責任幫輕父母，每份工作都值得尊重。<br />\n為父母不計較魚腥味<br />\nApple劏起魚來手起刀落，功架十足。21歲的她終日與魚檔為伴，毫不介意被人稱呼「賣魚妹」，其實中學時卻對因父母經營魚檔感到自卑。早在中一時，Apple閑餘時間幫忙看檔，回到學校卻經常因身上有魚腥味而被同學嘲笑。<br />\n直至中四那年，父母手部受傷，無人看檔，一時之間找不到人幫忙，Apple惟有硬著頭皮頂上。那是她第一次落手劏魚，連開檔、收檔都要「一腳踢」，經此一役，她才體會到父母經營魚檔是多麼辛苦，也令她對賣魚這個行業改觀。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n兩條片啲view數<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cbb5c610214339b298e1ef9e40863a89c9db47d","tid":1048456,"uid":135867,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T16:22:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dda1548ca5f2c7722854ee83746de80f7fce98b","tid":1048456,"uid":236401,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T16:25:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c93e9860d83e3779200adcae3222798fdfe0b4a8","tid":1048456,"uid":28624,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T16:30:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f1a947e5cad9ce5d826be9cb5e375161929dc18","tid":1048456,"uid":135867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T17:31:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97e9ac188a0494c16d0190901e81a4bdd31693a","tid":1048456,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T23:50:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5790cc624f364b99bc8ea88e6aafd20f07402110","tid":1048456,"uid":3063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-05T23:56:42.000Z","msg":"腥西<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"788b78a23cb352d4e320a67833a2eefd65db77c9","tid":1048456,"uid":53421,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T00:02:23.000Z","msg":"咁撚豬就收皮喇"},{"pid":"ba212ca62da6b1441961a34f2a0972e9b6f312c8","tid":1048456,"uid":47966,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-06T00:10:58.000Z","msg":"出面撈唔掂要靠老豆老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}